description: This source file implements the Teleco Voice Manager Call Control logic, including functions to get/set table entries and parameters, validate, commit, rollback configuration changes, and retrieve various call control statistics. It manages call lines, extensions, and their associated metrics, interacting with hardware abstraction layers and internal data structures to provide the necessary control and monitoring functionalities.
